        <mxCell id="z3kOPlYkljQr6b6lWWEr-7" value="&lt;div&gt;&lt;font style=&quot;font-size: 14px&quot;&gt;&lt;u&gt;&lt;b&gt;Important terms&lt;/b&gt;&lt;/u&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div&gt;1. &lt;u&gt;&lt;b&gt;Exercise price&lt;/b&gt;&lt;/u&gt; = the concessional price at the right to a share is give to the employee&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div&gt;2. &lt;u&gt;&lt;b&gt;market price / fair value&lt;/b&gt;&lt;/u&gt; = the price of the share in the market. the price employee had to pay if he had bought in the market&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div&gt;3. &lt;u&gt;&lt;b&gt;Intrinsic value&lt;/b&gt;&lt;/u&gt; = market price / fair value - Exercise price&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div&gt;[the difference in the exercise price and the market price]&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div&gt;4. &lt;u&gt;&lt;b&gt;face value&lt;/b&gt;&lt;/u&gt; = the face value share issued by the company.&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div&gt;5. &lt;u&gt;&lt;b&gt;Grant date&lt;/b&gt;&lt;/u&gt; =&amp;nbsp; date when employee and the company entry into ESOP contract.&lt;br&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div&gt;6. &lt;u&gt;&lt;b&gt;Vesting period&lt;/b&gt;&lt;/u&gt; = the duration/amount of time the employee has to work uninterrupted in the company.&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div&gt;7. &lt;u&gt;&lt;b&gt;Exercise period&lt;/b&gt;&lt;/u&gt; = the period in which the employee has to buy the shares. exercise period comes after fulfilling the vesting period. if the shares are not purchased within the exercise period then the ESOP for those shares will get lapsed&lt;br&gt;&lt;/div&gt;" style="rounded=1;whiteSpace=wrap;html=1;arcSize=4;" vertex="1" parent="1">
